</div>
<div>
<p>
<date notBefore="1094" notAfter="1098">紹聖</date>初<pc>，</pc>入為吏部<term>尚書</term>
<pc>，</pc>上疏乞依<date notBefore="1078" notAfter="1085">元豐</date>詔<pc>，</pc>定北郊夏至親祀<pc>。</pc>拜<term>
<term>尚書</term>左丞</term>
