</div>
<div>
<p>
<date notBefore="1086" notAfter="1094">元祐</date>末<pc>，</pc>以兵部<term>尚書</term>召<pc>。</pc>
<date notBefore="1094" notAfter="1098">紹聖</date>初<pc>，</pc>哲宗親政<pc>，</pc>
